.PP 
a port needs to be redrawn (\fIGUI Only\fP) 

Generated by the GraphicsManager whenever it is time to redraw a Port\&. All drawing calls should be done during the handling of a \fBpdg\&.eventType_PortDraw\fP\&. 
.PP
.nf
{ 
    emitter: {},       // the emitter that generated this event
    eventType: 24,     // the event type (eventType_PortDraw)
