.SH "struct pdg::SoundEvent"
.PP 
a sound completed or is looping (\fIGUI Only\fP) 

Generated by the SoundManager whenever a sound finishes playing (\fBpdg\&.soundEvent_DonePlaying\fP), or reaches the end and loops (\fBpdg\&.soundEvent_Looping\fP)\&. If there is an error, you will get eventCode \fBpdg\&.soundEvent_FailedToPlay\fP

.PP
For keyboard data entry, use \fBpdg\&.eventType_KeyPress\fP\&. 
.PP
.nf
{ 
    emitter: {},       // the emitter that generated this event
    eventType: 14,     // the event type (eventType_SoundEvent)
    eventCode: 0,      // the sound event code (one of: soundEvent_DonePlaying(0), 

.fi
.PP
 soundEvent_Looping(1), or soundEvent_FailedToPlay(2)) sound: {} // the Sound object that caused the event }

